Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please listen to their ideas and tell us what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are the mystery masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Nakajou Jun'ya, the vice-director from the filming team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Haba Tomohiro from the prop team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawakiguchi Misaki from the marketing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she taking this seriously at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll leave this in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come get us later, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry fer gettin' ya mixed up in this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We mighta started on a whim but it'd be a shame if we couldn't finish it, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope ya'll help us a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are whisky candies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sample of a new product.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on the filming team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a hard time with the shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The actors had a fun time improvisin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:39.16,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1232,520)\blur3\bord1\clip(586,554,603,599)\t(0,1232,\clip(586,554,1280,599)\t(4110,4630,\clip(1280,554,1280,599)))\pos(993,557)}Murder in the Ghost Town of Furuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gettin' there was a job and a half, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Took over an hour by bus 'n' train.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd it hafta be in the middle o' nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}was{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It caught a few people's fancy 'cos it looked interestin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Narakubo is basically a ghost town, right? How'd you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's-her-face talked to the caretaker 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, that's all I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Hongou, the scriptwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not doin' so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that anyone blames her or anythin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she particularly frail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She missed school a bunch of times and didn't come to the shootings either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess she was working on the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the team not like Hongou's script?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one complained! Not a bad word was said 'bout it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people in charge wanted to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha gettin' at? We all approved of Hongou's work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course I did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hongou tell you anything about who the culprit might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as far as I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kounosu told us to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And did you ask the actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone heard anything relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if the twist was something physical? Or a trick of the mind?{that eyebrow}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how 'bout listenin' to my idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya ask me, a script don't need no twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all 'bout the excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just solve the case somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch the culprit confess, cryin' like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That oughta do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.24,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an2\blur1.5\fs200\c&H040404&\yshad6\xshad4\fnOptimusPrincepsSemiBold\b1\4c&HF1F0F1&\frx90\fry0\t(0,984,\frx0\blur0.5\pos(200,466)}Fin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:43.87,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an2\blur0.5\fs200\c&H040404&\yshad6\xshad4\fnOptimusPrincepsSemiBold\b1\4c&HF1F0F1&\pos(200,466)}Fin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaitou's death was pretty excitin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A rip-roarin' death for the proud leader o' the prop team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Real nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You improvised that scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're all so obsessed with that crap,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the rules of mystery or whatever. Drama's where it's at!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, the title's gotta lay it bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Murder in the Ghost Town of Furuoka."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:14.19,dicks,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\c&H2D1D9C&\pos(618,193)\t(2736,3987,\c&H281CE3&)}Murder {\alpha&HFF&\t(275,275,\alpha&H00)}in {\alpha&HFF&\t(525,525,\alpha&H00)}the \N{\alpha&HFF&\t(775,775,\alpha&H00)}Ghost {\alpha&HFF&\t(1026,1026,\alpha&H00)}Town \N{\alpha&HFF&\t(1276,1276,\alpha&H00)}of {\alpha&HFF&\t(1526,1526,\alpha&H00)}Furu{\alpha&HFF&\t(1818,1818,\alpha&H00)}oka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...or somethin' like that, so folks come 'n' see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou must've known that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, what's your theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he died, what was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A locked room murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaitou died in a room with all exits locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{sate}So how'd the culprit kill him? Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{deru}How'd he get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece o' cake! The window!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The window?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The culprit escaped through the window after killin' Kaitou, clear as day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The window? Sorry, my memory's a bit hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, got the floor plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaitou died here, in the stage's left wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The other characters entered here, from the right corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The door was locked, so someone had to go get the master key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they entered the left wing, Kaitou was lying there dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The doors to the stage and the crossover were blocked by junk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the only possible exits were these:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The door they came in by and the left wing's window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But did Hongou know that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's an important point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hongou wrote the script just based on the floor plan, without seeing the place for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then she might've intended the murderer to take another route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry 'bout that. Before she wrote the script, she surveyed the location once herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In June... or was it the end of May?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that window's how the culprit came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And there ya have it. That's how Kaitou died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Howzat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be a pretty boring mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Hongou 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like she knows anythin' 'bout mysteries either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt she woulda come up with some cool twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But then who was the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the murderer's identity is the twist? Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And after everyone entered the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't there a shot showing what was outside the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was clear that no one left through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone had walked through that sea of grass, it'd be bent out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no such evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they could have escaped through the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou might've just forgotten 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you use that argument it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I heard that Hongou paid great attention to realism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, Hongou went there 'round the end of May!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The grass must've grown out after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she thought the window'd work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But then we just gotta cut the grass
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and retake from the corpse scene at the next shooting, and it'll all match up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! Howzat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit escaped through the window! It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that really be it? That's not much of a twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At least it's physically possible, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Nakajou's theory was what Hongou really intended?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some trouble accepting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right in that Nakajou's theory is contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There's a contradiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple resolution, but it flies in the face of common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a roundabout way to put it, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fitting for the detective, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what exactly do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the culprit's shoes. There's no way he'd enter through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If he entered through the window, he'd risk crossing someone's line of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, or here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If he entered from outside the building then someone would see him for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,especially during broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were the culprit, I wouldn't have gone in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the long and short of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know if Hongou thought the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if we can read Hongou's script, we can find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you guys read much crime fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized while listening to Nakajou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone has their own idea of what a "mystery novel" is.{jp is 推理モノ lit. logic novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His way of thinking certainly {\i1}was{\i0} novel.{dohoho}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lot. Read a few, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual. Agatha Christie and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single one? At all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really enjoy mysteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried enough to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read any for years, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku is trying to be a real Sherlockian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Sherlockian?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that refers to Sherlock Holmes' enthusiastic fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really enthusiastic fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sherlockian" means something a bit different...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've refuted Nakajou's theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we see the script? We'd like to know how much detail Hongou put in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll go to look for it. In the meantime, please talk to Haba Tomohiro from the prop team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you chaps might be up for a little tête-à-tête regarding mysteries.
