Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us too, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, it's quite well written.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, rather detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Be sure not to disturb the tall grass outside the window."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So she did consider it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what about the last person, Sawakiguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Sawakiguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciao to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, at marketing we're in like, such a bind without the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even finish the posters, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna just see that script over and done with already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hongou volunteer to write the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Majority vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who decided that it'd be a mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a vote, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And who decided to make a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we getting a bit off-topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the minutes of our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out if you think it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to my theory, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you guys to think of the word "mystery" and tell me what you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Orient Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a detective novel! Pretty hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you asked for "mystery" in a video rental shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd usually get stuff like Friday the 13th or Nightmare on Elm Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't those horror fi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it like someone who isn't interested in the genre.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.48,notebook,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(367,443)}No 31. What should the murder weapon be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.48,notebook,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(425,424)}Knife (stabbing) - 10
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.48,notebook,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(508,462)}Rope (strangulation) - 8
